---
title: Saucy Tikka-Style Chicken Breasts Sandwiches with Indian-Spiced Potatoes
description: There's nothing basic about this chicken sandwich! Tangy  salad and chicken breasts coated in fragrant tikka sauce are the perfect combo, all wrapped up in a soft bun. On the side, Indian-spiced roasted potatoes are yours for the dipping into a DIY tikka mayo.
